    { title: "Project profitability is a guess until close", description: "Scope creep happens, hours are over, and you find out the retainer made $200/hr instead of $400/hr — too late to fix." },
    { title: "Client reports are hand-built every month", description: "Account managers stitch reports from 6 platforms into a Google Slide. It's nobody's favorite Tuesday." },
    { title: "Retainers churn quietly", description: "The CSAT signal exists in client meetings, but nothing operational triggers an intervention until renewal time." },
