    { question: "Do you replace HubSpot / ClickUp / Asana / Harvest?", answer: "Usually no — we wrap them. We integrate with your existing CRM, PM and time tool to fix the seams between new business, delivery and finance. For larger agencies we sometimes consolidate onto a custom spine." },
    { question: "Can you support project + retainer + product mixed business models?", answer: "Yes. We model project work, ongoing retainers, productized services and one-off engagements with distinct profitability rules and renewal mechanics." },
    { question: "How does pricing / scoping logic work?", answer: "We build a pricing engine that mirrors your scoping math — by role, by hour, by package — so proposals are fast, consistent and margin-aware before the SOW goes out." },
    { question: "Will the team actually fill in time?", answer: "We design time capture to be passive: pulled from calendar, tools and project events, with a quick daily review. Designers don't fill timesheets — they approve them." },
